    Serializable, Cloneable, Comparable<ApprovalProfile>, org.cesecore.internal.IUpgradeableData, org.cesecore.profiles.Profile, ApprovalProfile
    public class AccumulativeApprovalProfile
extends ApprovalProfileBase
    This approval archetype represents the legacy method of approvals, i.e where a fixed number of administrators need to approve a request for it to pass.
    Version:
